---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import armscollection2 from '../../assets/Photos/cuddapah/armscollection2.jpg';
import annualsportsmeetkr2 from '../../assets/Photos/karimnagar/annualsportsmeetkr2.jpg';
import cricket1 from '../../assets/Photos/warangal/cricket1.jpg';
import pulivendlaoffice1 from '../../assets/Photos/cuddapah/pulivendlaoffice1.jpg';
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Career Highlights</h1>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-4">
        <li class="mb-2">Raised the standards of policing and administration for his fellow officers to emulate.</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Provided a strict, yet fair administration, turning around the negative image of the police.</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Bold and daring in dealing with naxalites, relentlessly pursuing and leading all counter-terrorist operations himself.</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Maintained a very high degree of honesty, integrity, and professionalism.</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Set a very high standard for himself and encouraged his fellow police officers to attain and excel.</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Raised the morale of the police force, instilling a sense of pride and confidence.</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Cared about the fellow human being, and his humane nature made him an instant favorite of the common man.</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Immersed himself in truly solving the real problems faced by the people, not limiting himself to police work alone.</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Adored by both the common man and the police in all the districts he worked.</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Looked after the well-being of all police officials working with him and supported their families in times of need.</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Ensured that election time violence became a thing of the past in all the districts he served.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-5">
        <div class="card">
            <Image src={armscollection2} alt="Arms Collection" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">Arms Collection</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <Image src={annualsportsmeetkr2} alt="Annual Sports Meet" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">Annual Sports Meet</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <Image src={cricket1} alt="Cricket" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">Cricket</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <Image src={pulivendlaoffice1} alt="Pulivendla Office" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">Pulivendla Office</p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
